peace package 
the presidents plan calls for shipments to poland of beef pork 
corn butter butter oil sunflower oil cotton and rice the new 
50 million infusion was in addition to 50 million in food bush 
announced in early august for the new fiscal year that begins oct 1 
it is on top of 84 million in emergency food assistance bush 
