pretty happy about it it would be nice to come back next year 
too 
some fishermen who suffered from a restricted salmon season and a 
poor catch say the sound will never be the same 
its time that everyone realizes that no amount of money in the 
world is going to restore prince william sound to a pristine 
condition said riki ott of cordova district fishermen united 
