accident near the westchester county community of katonah the 
couple lived in south salem 
fabricant was professor emeritus of economics at new york 
university where he began teaching in 1946 he also was director 
emeritus of the national bureau of economics research where he was 
associated with the economist and presidential adviser arthur burns 
fabricants research made him one of the top authorities on what 
causes a recession he also wrote extensively on such topics as 
