the companys 360 employees were counseled in offices that had been 
cleaned up overnight bullet holes in walls and ceilings were the 
only physical reminders of the tragedy 
until it strikes home like it has for us you dont realize how 
traumatic something like this can be shea said im pleased to 
say that so far the counseling has gone very well 
pressman tom noonan said the workers were split up into groups 
with some receiving oneonone counseling 
you just vented your feelings noonan said 
