the service attended by about 300 people 
three of the wounded were in critical condition friday at humana 
hospitaluniversity of louisville including one man shot in the 
chest and leg who was back in surgery friday afternoon 
the bloodshed started in the plants executive offices on the 
third floor moved down to the basement then up to the first floor 
